Funke Akindele Calls Out Her Husband After Romance Video On Internet As romantic videos of a newly married couple emerge online, Nollywood box office queen Funke Akindele Bello weeps for her husband. When a video of a newly married young couple went viral, the internet went crazy, according to Kemi Filani News. The couple was captured kissing passionately on their wedding day in a viral video, leaving the church congregation speechless. Funke shared the video on her Instagram story, asking for her husband’s whereabouts. Wow!!! she wrote. I adore it! Where have you gone, @jjcskillz? READ ALSO: Uche Maduagwu Abuses Funke Akindele After She Gave Out Pair Of Shoe Funke got social media gushing a few days ago when she shared loved-up photos with her husband, according to Kemi Filani. Similarly, her husband posted the same photos with a caption that went viral on the internet. @funkejenifaakindele, just the two of us, we can make it if we try, he wrote. It should also be remembered that Funke Akindele’s absence from Eniola Badmus’ 20th anniversary party drew mixed reactions from Nigerians, and she has remained silent since then.